ba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth was born in 1240, in Scotland. She had at least 1 son with Robert de Lawedre."},"et":{"1240–":"1240–Surnud","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Female":"1240–Surnud","1337":"1337","1235":"1235","1311":"1311","1263":"1263","1240":"1240","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fi":{"1240–":"1240–Kuollut","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Female":"1240–Kuollut","1337":"1337","1235":"1235","1311":"1311","1263":"1263","1240":"1240","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fr":{"1240–":"1240–Décédée","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Female":"1240–Décédée","1337":"1337","1235":"1235","1311":"1311","1263":"1263","1240":"1240","Scotland":"Écosse","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth est née en 1240, à Écosse. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Robert de Lawedre."},"de":{"1240–":"1240–Verstorben","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Female":"1240–Verstorben","1337":"1337","1235":"1235","1311":"1311","1263":"1263","1240":"1240","Scotland":"Scotland","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth wurde 1240 in Scotland geboren. Sie hatte mit Robert de Lawedre mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1240–":"1240–Desede","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Female":"1240–Desede","1337":"1337","1235":"1235","1311":"1311","1263":"1263","1240":"1240","Scotland":"Scotland"},"hu":{"1240–":"1240–elhunyt","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Female":"1240–elhunyt","1337":"1337","1235":"1235","1311":"1311","1263":"1263","1240":"1240","Scotland":"Scotland"},"id":{"1240–":"1240–Telah Meninggal","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Female":"1240–Telah Meninggal","1337":"1337","1235":"1235","1311":"1311","1263":"1263","1240":"1240","Scotland":"Scotland"},"it":{"1240–":"1240–Deceduta","1235–1311":"1235–1311","1263–1337":"1263–1337","1240–Fema